1
00:00:02,390 --> 00:00:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Morning, Milkit.</font>

2
00:00:04,340 --> 00:00:07,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Good morning, Master.</font>

3
00:00:10,400 --> 00:00:12,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll go get changed.</font>

4
00:00:12,240 --> 00:00:13,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

5
00:00:13,030 --> 00:00:15,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll be waiting, Master.</font>

6
00:00:22,560 --> 00:00:24,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Wait, you'll keep wearing 
your bandages?</i></font>

7
00:00:26,990 --> 00:00:29,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they help you feel better, it's fine.</font>

8
00:00:29,670 --> 00:00:31,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry if I made you uncomfortable.</font>

9
00:00:31,900 --> 00:00:37,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What if I say I'll take them off 
when it's just the two of us?</font>

10
00:00:37,990 --> 00:00:40,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just the two of us...</font>

11
00:00:44,460 --> 00:00:46,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Stare...</i></font>

12
00:00:46,610 --> 00:00:49,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What is it, Eterna?</font>

13
00:00:49,450 --> 00:00:53,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You look like a teenage boy 
on the eve of his first date.</font>

14
00:00:54,590 --> 00:00:58,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wh-What kinda comparison is that? 
I don't get it at all!</font>

15
00:00:58,630 --> 00:01:00,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't get what's happening either.</font>

16
00:01:01,870 --> 00:01:04,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Milkit's face is fine now.</font>

17
00:01:04,020 --> 00:01:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I said it was okay 
to take the bandages off.</font>

18
00:01:06,630 --> 00:01:10,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why, then, is she still bandaged up?</font>

19
00:01:10,090 --> 00:01:14,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that? Why indeed...</font>

20
00:01:14,380 --> 00:01:16,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah. I think I get it now.</font>

21
00:01:16,730 --> 00:01:18,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something smells nice!</font>

22
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:21,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's a hot sandwich with fried eggs.</font>

23
00:01:21,480 --> 00:01:23,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You seemed to have taken 
a real liking to them, Ink.</font>

24
00:01:23,770 --> 00:01:26,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow! I love you, Milkit!</font>

25
00:01:31,700 --> 00:01:32,450
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}STAB STAB</b></font>

26
00:01:31,830 --> 00:01:33,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What's this stabbing pain in my chest?</i></font>

27
00:01:34,150 --> 00:01:36,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>My Milkit...</i></font>

28
00:01:36,330 --> 00:01:36,950
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}STAB STAB</b></font>

29
00:01:37,200 --> 00:01:37,950
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}STAB STAB</b></font>

30
00:01:38,070 --> 00:01:38,700
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}STAB STAB</b></font>

31
00:01:41,310 --> 00:01:42,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Rest in peace.</font>

32
00:01:44,540 --> 00:01:46,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Flum?</font>

33
00:01:46,500 --> 00:01:48,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you all right, Master?</font>

34
00:01:48,940 --> 00:01:52,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't worry about her. She's just 
been possessed by her possessiveness.</font>

35
00:03:22,970 --> 00:03:25,730
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}FAMILY
SOLITUDE</b></font>

36
00:03:25,730 --> 00:03:27,980
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}SOLITUDE AND FAMILY</b></font>

37
00:03:29,620 --> 00:03:32,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm pretty sure 
today's job is around here.</font>

38
00:03:34,270 --> 00:03:36,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is this stench?</font>

39
00:03:39,820 --> 00:03:42,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Excuse me. Let me through.</font>

40
00:03:45,630 --> 00:03:49,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>There she found grotesque monsters, 
still alive and writhing.</i></font>

41
00:03:49,460 --> 00:03:52,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They had arms, legs, and faces,</i></font>

42
00:03:52,970 --> 00:03:56,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>but none of them were 
where they should have been,</i></font>

43
00:03:56,980 --> 00:03:59,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and the numbers were all off.</i></font>

44
00:03:59,840 --> 00:04:02,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>These were but lumps of flesh 
that used to be human not long ago.</i></font>

45
00:04:03,380 --> 00:04:04,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This way.</font>

46
00:04:05,290 --> 00:04:07,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Ed and Jonny...</i></font>

47
00:04:10,060 --> 00:04:12,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We'll take care of these.</font>

48
00:04:12,480 --> 00:04:15,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You guys get the crowd away from here.</font>

49
00:04:15,590 --> 00:04:16,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? But...</font>

50
00:04:18,630 --> 00:04:20,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't want any more panic.</font>

51
00:04:23,370 --> 00:04:24,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Understood, sir.</font>

52
00:04:26,190 --> 00:04:29,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Apparently, the Church 
is looking into those... things.</font>

53
00:04:30,210 --> 00:04:31,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On paper, at least.</font>

54
00:04:32,840 --> 00:04:37,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Normally, church knights from a nearby 
station show up when there's an incident.</font>

55
00:04:38,440 --> 00:04:40,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But those guys today?</font>

56
00:04:41,150 --> 00:04:44,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their gear marked them as bein' 
way higher up the ladder.</font>

57
00:04:44,570 --> 00:04:47,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And when I scanned them, 
they were pretty much all B-Rank.</font>

58
00:04:47,890 --> 00:04:50,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were knights from 
the pope's inner circle.</font>

59
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:58,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Meanin' those guys were here to cover up 
somethin' inconvenient for the Church.</font>

60
00:05:00,210 --> 00:05:03,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Church pulled strings 
to get a gag order issued.</font>

61
00:05:03,620 --> 00:05:05,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It was swept under the rug.</font>

62
00:05:06,340 --> 00:05:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is an extraordinary case,</font>

63
00:05:08,160 --> 00:05:12,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">so they may have just sent powerful 
knights because of the danger involved.</font>

64
00:05:12,380 --> 00:05:15,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We still have absolutely 
no clue what those things were.</font>

65
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so...?</font>

66
00:05:18,030 --> 00:05:21,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also, you probably shouldn't be 
out and about for the time being.</font>

67
00:05:21,420 --> 00:05:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. Who knows where those 
eyeballs could be lyin' in wait?</font>

68
00:05:25,430 --> 00:05:26,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eyeballs?</font>

69
00:05:26,790 --> 00:05:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">According to witnesses, the victims were 
attacked by a large flock of eyeballs.</font>

70
00:05:34,780 --> 00:05:38,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Eyeballs attacked them... 
and turned them into that?</i></font>

71
00:05:38,740 --> 00:05:40,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>What does that even mean?</i></font>

72
00:05:41,420 --> 00:05:43,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And the Church has a gag order out?</i></font>

73
00:05:43,220 --> 00:05:45,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Could it be related to 
their secret research?</i></font>

74
00:05:47,310 --> 00:05:51,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I see! So there really is a Church 
research facility in the capital, too!</i></font>

75
00:06:00,850 --> 00:06:02,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The Church and its research...</i></font>

76
00:06:03,270 --> 00:06:06,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>How do I protect myself from that?</i></font>

77
00:06:07,720 --> 00:06:09,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Protect," huh?</font>

78
00:06:10,650 --> 00:06:12,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Back when I was in the heroes' party,</i></font>

79
00:06:12,550 --> 00:06:15,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'd get targeted first 
because I was the weakest.</i></font>

80
00:06:15,010 --> 00:06:17,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cyrill was the one 
who'd always bail me out.</i></font>

81
00:06:19,070 --> 00:06:20,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Now that I can fight too,</i></font>

82
00:06:21,400 --> 00:06:22,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I feel like...</i></font>

83
00:06:22,900 --> 00:06:27,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Cyrill must've been 
anxious deep down, too.</i></font>

84
00:06:32,730 --> 00:06:34,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>But if she was,</i></font>

85
00:06:35,170 --> 00:06:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>how was she able to fight like that?</i></font>

86
00:06:40,270 --> 00:06:44,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Meanwhile, I get worried sick 
that I might not be up to the task.</i></font>

87
00:06:46,190 --> 00:06:48,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I don't intend to pick 
a fight with the Church.</i></font>

88
00:06:49,330 --> 00:06:53,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I just want to protect 
the people I care about.</i></font>

89
00:06:56,060 --> 00:06:58,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I wonder what Cyrill's up to now.</font>

90
00:07:02,390 --> 00:07:06,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We failed to reach our 
planned destination yet again.</font>

91
00:07:08,170 --> 00:07:10,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is all because I'm weak.</font>

92
00:07:10,340 --> 00:07:13,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't need to 
feel responsible, Cyrill.</font>

93
00:07:14,820 --> 00:07:17,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let Jean stew in his own frustration.</font>

94
00:07:18,020 --> 00:07:23,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I cast Flum aside, but as soon as she 
was gone, I lost the ability to fight.</i></font>

95
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm the lowest of the low.</font>

96
00:07:27,470 --> 00:07:29,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Leave the party?</font>

97
00:07:29,820 --> 00:07:30,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

98
00:07:30,850 --> 00:07:33,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum and Eterna are both gone, anyway.</font>

99
00:07:33,510 --> 00:07:36,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What will we do after we leave?</font>

100
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:42,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, we could travel the world 
and check out all my favorite sights.</font>

101
00:07:43,440 --> 00:07:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That sounds like 
a wonderful journey. But...</font>

102
00:07:47,350 --> 00:07:51,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I can't pursue my own happiness 
until the demons are exterminated"?</font>

103
00:07:52,110 --> 00:07:53,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Linus?</font>

104
00:07:54,780 --> 00:07:55,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry!</font>

105
00:07:55,740 --> 00:07:57,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I looked into it!</font>

106
00:07:57,660 --> 00:08:00,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you know about my hometown?</font>

107
00:08:00,860 --> 00:08:05,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah. I found out it was destroyed 
by demons ten years ago.</font>

108
00:08:06,640 --> 00:08:07,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Correct.</font>

109
00:08:08,570 --> 00:08:14,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The demons stabbed, tore apart, 
crushed, and burned my loved ones,</font>

110
00:08:15,320 --> 00:08:17,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and I remember 
every last bit of that sight.</font>

111
00:08:19,370 --> 00:08:23,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They are disgusting monsters 
that can kill with a smile.</font>

112
00:08:24,480 --> 00:08:26,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They are an evil that must be destroyed.</font>

113
00:08:27,750 --> 00:08:28,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maria...</font>

114
00:08:30,530 --> 00:08:33,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I do not wish to lose anyone else 
who is dear to me.</font>

115
00:08:34,730 --> 00:08:37,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Some of them are in the capital.</font>

116
00:08:38,290 --> 00:08:42,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Th-That wouldn't happen 
to include a lover, would it?</font>

117
00:08:45,550 --> 00:08:50,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're like family to me. A younger 
sister, and an older and younger brother.</font>

118
00:08:51,270 --> 00:08:52,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is that so...?</font>

119
00:08:52,670 --> 00:08:53,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is.</font>

120
00:08:56,790 --> 00:08:58,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's odd.</font>

121
00:09:00,360 --> 00:09:03,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm getting a strange reading 
specifically from her heart.</i></font>

122
00:09:06,540 --> 00:09:10,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Say, Eterna. What are these floaty things?</font>

123
00:09:10,770 --> 00:09:15,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mana-Optimizing Floating Objects. 
They're devices that boost mana.</font>

124
00:09:15,790 --> 00:09:18,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Devices? They're not living things?</font>

125
00:09:18,740 --> 00:09:21,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But they're so friendly.</font>

126
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:24,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">After years of use, 
they started to gain individuality.</font>

127
00:09:24,740 --> 00:09:26,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're like my buddies now.</font>

128
00:09:26,920 --> 00:09:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I give them names?</font>

129
00:09:30,920 --> 00:09:34,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you answer my questions, sure.</font>

130
00:09:34,770 --> 00:09:38,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I-I told you I have amnesia.</font>

131
00:09:38,210 --> 00:09:40,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno if I have the answers you want.</font>

132
00:09:40,640 --> 00:09:42,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just answer what you can.</font>

133
00:09:42,710 --> 00:09:46,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have a sickness 
of the heart or something?</font>

134
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:49,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? My heart?</font>

135
00:09:49,070 --> 00:09:50,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't think so.</font>

136
00:09:50,490 --> 00:09:52,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you taking any medicine, then?</font>

137
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:54,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

138
00:09:55,550 --> 00:09:57,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not.</font>

139
00:09:58,480 --> 00:10:00,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Got it.</font>

140
00:10:00,400 --> 00:10:03,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I answered your questions. 
Can I give this one a name now?</font>

141
00:10:03,580 --> 00:10:05,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like what?</font>

142
00:10:05,140 --> 00:10:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm... It's a Mana-Optimizing 
Floating Object, so...</font>

143
00:10:10,040 --> 00:10:11,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Mofo!</font>

144
00:10:14,440 --> 00:10:15,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope.</font>

145
00:10:17,270 --> 00:10:19,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Let's eat!</font>

146
00:10:19,480 --> 00:10:22,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? Sara, those guys 
who always come to get you</font>

147
00:10:22,770 --> 00:10:25,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">aren't your real brothers?</font>

148
00:10:25,100 --> 00:10:30,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nope. I didn't have any family, 
so Ed and Jonny took over the role.</font>

149
00:10:31,110 --> 00:10:36,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're like brothers who looked after me.</font>

150
00:10:36,940 --> 00:10:39,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, that reminds me. Ed and Jonny...</font>

151
00:10:40,020 --> 00:10:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They were worried about you today.</font>

152
00:10:43,150 --> 00:10:45,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With all this dangerous stuff 
happening lately,</font>

153
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't want Sara out and about so much.</font>

154
00:10:50,530 --> 00:10:53,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She doesn't listen to us no more.</font>

155
00:10:55,110 --> 00:10:58,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It scares me how reckless she's bein'.</font>

156
00:10:59,510 --> 00:11:02,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, it's our job to keep her safe.</font>

157
00:11:03,270 --> 00:11:08,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I think you should 
stop annoying her, though.</font>

158
00:11:08,540 --> 00:11:14,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You say they worry about me, but Ed 
enjoys annoyin' me by messin' up my hair,</font>

159
00:11:14,500 --> 00:11:16,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Jonny's overprotective.</font>

160
00:11:16,570 --> 00:11:20,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Besides, <i>I'm</i> the one 
who's worried about <i>them</i>.</font>

161
00:11:20,130 --> 00:11:23,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ed's always actin' without 
thinkin' whenever I'm involved,</font>

162
00:11:23,980 --> 00:11:27,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Jonny always puts himself 
second after me.</font>

163
00:11:28,130 --> 00:11:32,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They keep treating me 
like a child forever.</font>

164
00:11:32,730 --> 00:11:36,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You all care deeply about one another. 
That's why you worry.</font>

165
00:11:36,920 --> 00:11:39,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You worry, even though 
you're not real family?</font>

166
00:11:39,930 --> 00:11:41,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh? O-Of course.</font>

167
00:11:42,700 --> 00:11:48,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ed, Jonny, me, and Maria all 
grew up together like family.</font>

168
00:11:48,260 --> 00:11:53,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you care and worry 'bout one another, 
that makes ya family in my books.</font>

169
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:57,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Also,</font>

170
00:11:57,940 --> 00:11:59,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Flum,</font>

171
00:11:59,830 --> 00:12:01,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Miss Milkit,</font>

172
00:12:01,900 --> 00:12:03,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eterna,</font>

173
00:12:03,630 --> 00:12:04,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Ink, too!</font>

174
00:12:05,240 --> 00:12:08,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're my friends, and I care about y'all 
as much as I would my own family!</font>

175
00:12:08,670 --> 00:12:12,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wow, I didn't know you felt that way.</font>

176
00:12:12,650 --> 00:12:16,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ed and Jonny need to hear 
what you just said, too.</font>

177
00:12:19,200 --> 00:12:23,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Over my dead body! It's too embarrassin'!</font>

178
00:12:27,210 --> 00:12:30,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Family... Friends...</font>

179
00:12:30,500 --> 00:12:32,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're utterly useless.</font>

180
00:12:32,940 --> 00:12:34,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You good-for-nothing!</font>

181
00:12:38,730 --> 00:12:40,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ink, it's me.</font>

182
00:12:40,530 --> 00:12:41,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Eterna?</font>

183
00:12:41,860 --> 00:12:43,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">May I come in?</font>

184
00:12:43,400 --> 00:12:44,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What is it?</font>

185
00:12:49,830 --> 00:12:50,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It should be ready.</font>

186
00:12:59,920 --> 00:13:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's sweet.</font>

187
00:13:04,110 --> 00:13:07,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When you're feeling down, 
rose tea really hits the spot.</font>

188
00:13:07,910 --> 00:13:11,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How did you know I was feeling down?</font>

189
00:13:11,750 --> 00:13:16,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Watching you reminds me 
of the old me and my family.</font>

190
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:22,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why I just can't leave you alone.</font>

191
00:13:23,690 --> 00:13:27,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The old Eterna?</font>

192
00:13:34,860 --> 00:13:36,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Curry?</font>

193
00:13:36,370 --> 00:13:37,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hamburg steak?</font>

194
00:13:37,840 --> 00:13:40,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Baked fish sounds good, too.</font>

195
00:13:41,070 --> 00:13:45,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, I can't wait for dinner tonight!</font>

196
00:13:45,980 --> 00:13:49,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dein and Kahnis 
are finally gonna face off.</font>

197
00:13:49,140 --> 00:13:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which one are you guys betting on?</font>

198
00:13:52,070 --> 00:13:54,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kahnis, obviously.</font>

199
00:13:54,350 --> 00:13:55,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What about you, Badras?</font>

200
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:58,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dein's still our leader.</font>

201
00:13:58,830 --> 00:14:04,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Knowing him, joining the Church of Origin 
has to be part of some master plan.</font>

202
00:14:04,040 --> 00:14:05,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's always had a plan, remember?</font>

203
00:14:07,200 --> 00:14:09,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's time. Let's go.</font>

204
00:14:20,190 --> 00:14:21,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Heya, Dein.</font>

205
00:14:23,380 --> 00:14:29,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry for making you take time out of 
your busy praying schedule to come here.</font>

206
00:14:30,000 --> 00:14:35,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Show him who the real boss 
of the West District is, Kahnis!</font>

207
00:14:37,160 --> 00:14:50,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Kahnis! Kahnis!</font>

208
00:14:43,540 --> 00:14:44,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's acting weird.</font>

209
00:14:44,900 --> 00:14:46,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's gotta be on some kinda drug.</font>

210
00:14:46,740 --> 00:14:49,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Maybe the stuff he was distributing 
to the royal army?</font>

211
00:14:50,610 --> 00:14:52,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This fight's as good as won.</font>

212
00:14:52,580 --> 00:14:55,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's the matter? 
Get high on your own supply?</font>

213
00:14:55,860 --> 00:14:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Victory is Kahnis's!</font>

214
00:14:58,080 --> 00:15:00,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dein! Please stand up, Dein!</font>

215
00:15:00,840 --> 00:15:04,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gents, as you see, the West District 
has a new boss as of today.</font>

216
00:15:04,840 --> 00:15:08,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And it's me, Kahnis Delphiny!</font>

217
00:15:09,440 --> 00:15:25,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Kahnis! Kahnis!</font>

218
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:18,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Pathetic. Is this really the guy 
who wanted to rule the West?</i></font>

219
00:15:18,590 --> 00:15:20,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Witness my compassion!</font>

220
00:15:20,770 --> 00:15:22,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll put you...</font>

221
00:15:23,580 --> 00:15:26,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">out of your misery!</font>

222
00:15:30,030 --> 00:15:32,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Keep your distance 
no matter what happens!</font>

223
00:15:32,910 --> 00:15:35,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Get out of there at the 
first sign of danger, Sara!</font>

224
00:15:36,100 --> 00:15:37,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Gotcha!</font>

225
00:15:37,750 --> 00:15:41,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Aw, you shouldn't have 
reached out like that.</font>

226
00:15:41,210 --> 00:15:45,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Relax. The next slash 
will send you to heaven.</font>

227
00:15:46,150 --> 00:15:50,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Among the countless voices in Dein's head</i></font>

228
00:15:50,210 --> 00:15:55,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>was one that seemed to whisper to him 
to stand up and kill his foe.</i></font>

229
00:16:05,820 --> 00:16:07,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-He's a monster...</font>

230
00:16:08,110 --> 00:16:11,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum... Apricot!</font>

231
00:16:11,780 --> 00:16:14,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I did it! I went and did it!</font>

232
00:16:15,170 --> 00:16:18,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd lost it all,</font>

233
00:16:18,460 --> 00:16:21,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but with sheer strength of will, 
with my own hands...</font>

234
00:16:21,790 --> 00:16:23,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I killed her!</font>

235
00:16:25,420 --> 00:16:29,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I killed Flum Apricot!</font>

236
00:16:31,100 --> 00:16:33,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Flum? What's he talking about?</font>

237
00:16:33,330 --> 00:16:34,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That was Kahnis!</font>

238
00:16:35,880 --> 00:16:38,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It... wasn't... Flum?</font>

239
00:16:42,550 --> 00:16:44,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kah...nis?</font>

240
00:16:52,970 --> 00:16:55,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is for Kahnis!</font>

241
00:16:55,810 --> 00:16:57,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Die...</font>

242
00:16:57,160 --> 00:16:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You monster!</font>

243
00:16:58,620 --> 00:17:02,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Monster! Monster! Monster!</font>

244
00:17:19,390 --> 00:17:22,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>They appeared out of nowhere.</i></font>

245
00:17:28,210 --> 00:17:31,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Once the eyeballs entered their bodies, 
it was all over for them.</i></font>

246
00:17:36,490 --> 00:17:40,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Countless heads, arms, and legs</i></font>

247
00:17:40,540 --> 00:17:42,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>grew from their twisted flesh.</i></font>

248
00:17:44,560 --> 00:17:45,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can hear them!</font>

249
00:17:46,310 --> 00:17:49,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Like bugs crawling through my brain!</font>

250
00:17:49,300 --> 00:17:52,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They swirl around in a spiraling vortex...</font>

251
00:17:52,540 --> 00:17:55,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ah! What the hell did you put in me?!</font>

252
00:17:55,930 --> 00:17:58,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Core, my ass! Children...?</font>

253
00:17:58,620 --> 00:18:02,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Divine... power?!</font>

254
00:18:02,120 --> 00:18:04,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my power!</font>

255
00:18:08,020 --> 00:18:09,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go away!</font>

256
00:18:16,680 --> 00:18:18,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run, you guys.</font>

257
00:18:28,120 --> 00:18:29,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're catching up!</font>

258
00:18:29,620 --> 00:18:31,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Run for your life!</font>

259
00:18:37,040 --> 00:18:38,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You two...</font>

260
00:18:42,310 --> 00:18:44,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go on ahead.</font>

261
00:18:44,910 --> 00:18:48,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That's what Miss Flum would say 
if she were in my shoes.</i></font>

262
00:18:49,130 --> 00:18:49,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No—</font>

263
00:18:49,680 --> 00:18:50,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No way!</font>

264
00:18:53,700 --> 00:18:54,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jonny!</font>

265
00:18:54,860 --> 00:18:56,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up and run!</font>

266
00:18:56,860 --> 00:18:59,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll buy you time!</font>

267
00:18:59,580 --> 00:19:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I could never...</font>

268
00:19:04,790 --> 00:19:07,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Jonny!</font>

269
00:19:07,460 --> 00:19:09,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ed, take care of Sara!</font>

270
00:19:09,920 --> 00:19:12,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Take care of our little sister!</font>

271
00:19:13,060 --> 00:19:15,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No! Jonny...</font>

272
00:19:15,130 --> 00:19:17,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You need to live as long as you can...</i></font>

273
00:19:17,440 --> 00:19:19,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>for his sake!</i></font>

274
00:19:24,310 --> 00:19:25,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We shook them off, huh?</font>

275
00:19:26,320 --> 00:19:27,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Thanks, Jonny.</font>

276
00:19:27,820 --> 00:19:30,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's my fault that he...</font>

277
00:19:33,540 --> 00:19:35,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know he doesn't regret a thing.</font>

278
00:19:36,140 --> 00:19:38,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He'd be happy to know he saved you.</font>

279
00:19:38,530 --> 00:19:40,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But... but...</font>

280
00:19:41,330 --> 00:19:44,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If I hadn't led you two there,</font>

281
00:19:45,530 --> 00:19:47,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">this woulda never happened!</font>

282
00:20:04,960 --> 00:20:06,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ed!</font>

283
00:20:08,720 --> 00:20:10,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I gave Jonny my word!</font>

284
00:20:11,560 --> 00:20:13,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you need to live!</font>

285
00:20:14,510 --> 00:20:17,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sara, I hope a small part of you remembers</i></font>

286
00:20:18,310 --> 00:20:21,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>that you had two super-awesome brothers.</i></font>

287
00:20:22,150 --> 00:20:26,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When you grow up, 
get married, wear that dress,</i></font>

288
00:20:26,550 --> 00:20:30,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>and look real pretty, 
I'll be there to mess up your hair.</i></font>

289
00:20:32,670 --> 00:20:34,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sara's late today.</font>

290
00:20:34,900 --> 00:20:36,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should we start without her?</font>

291
00:20:39,590 --> 00:20:40,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No.</font>

292
00:20:40,760 --> 00:20:43,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can eat once she's here.</font>

293
00:20:44,590 --> 00:20:46,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sara desperately fled for her life.</i></font>

294
00:20:48,020 --> 00:20:50,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Jonny... Ed...</font>

295
00:20:48,540 --> 00:20:53,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So that the despair of losing her family—
her loved ones—to a gruesome death</i></font>

296
00:20:54,690 --> 00:20:56,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>didn't swallow her whole.</i></font>

297
00:21:05,940 --> 00:21:09,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm gonna live.</font>

298
00:21:14,430 --> 00:21:15,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For Jonny...</font>

299
00:21:18,130 --> 00:21:19,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">and Ed, too...</font>

300
00:21:21,230 --> 00:21:22,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll live.</font>

301
00:21:24,260 --> 00:21:25,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll live...</font>

302
00:21:28,750 --> 00:21:30,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">a full life!</font>

303
00:21:44,230 --> 00:21:45,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's wrong, Sara?</font>

304
00:21:45,960 --> 00:21:47,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Didja have a bad dream?</font>

305
00:21:49,150 --> 00:21:53,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>After apologizing silently 
to everyone she knew,</i></font>

306
00:21:53,150 --> 00:21:55,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>she took one last look at the skies 
and closed her eyes.</i></font>

307
00:21:56,300 --> 00:22:01,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A fresh breeze, wholly unfitting 
of the dirty alley she was in,</i></font>

308
00:22:01,820 --> 00:22:03,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>gently caressed her cheeks.</i></font>

309
00:22:05,470 --> 00:22:10,180
<font face="Times New Roman" size="14"><b>{\an9}Translation: Sriram Gurunathan</b></font>

310
00:22:10,480 --> 00:22:15,190
<font face="Times New Roman" size="14"><b>{\an9}Subtitle Editing: Geoff Mazzolini

Subtitle Timing: Krzysztof Kunc</b></font>

311
00:22:15,490 --> 00:22:20,200
<font face="Times New Roman" size="14"><b>{\an9}Quality Check: Riley Dalton

Translation Check: Rei Miyasaka</b></font>

312
00:23:37,600 --> 00:23:39,940
<font size="22"><b>{\an8}TRUTH AND REALITY</b></font>

